{"tid":824323,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"勁過阿爸！小C朗又有波入！","createTime":"2018-09-17T04:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T15:54:56.000Z","uid":161311,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"91cae806178b751ccde5454ad694124dc6799837","tid":824323,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T04:43:39.000Z","msg":"基斯坦奴朗拿度在周末前仍未找到加盟祖雲達斯後的首個入球，不過其囝囝已經為「祖記」再入2球！<br />\n<br />\n         同樣都是加盟祖記，乃父基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）在今個周末的比賽前仍是顆粒無收，但效力祖記U8 的小C朗（Cristiano Jr）繼處子戰入夠4球之後，今周又有進帳！在C朗女友洛迪古絲的IG story中可見這個小C朗的入球甚有乃父影子，皮球美妙地彎入網中，引起場內觀眾的歡呼聲。 C朗對兒子的表現滿意之餘，更認為他可以繼承自己的衣缽：「他非常有競爭力，與少時的我十分相似，我們都不肯認輸。可能我會教他一點秘技，但要視乎他想不想我教。我當然希望他成為足球員，他有潛質，有速度、有技術，射球亦出色。」"},{"pid":"64af02d5b9b1e290307b6ebe911f414fe69335c2","tid":824323,"uid":81037,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:10:58.000Z","msg":"王騎會唔會反埋"},{"pid":"4c24031da5739489f29a819dd7624e154d51ab85","tid":824323,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/66e/1f8/66e1f87bb166f7885793d934edd13bee574d242b_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F66e%2F1f8%2F66e1f87bb166f7885793d934edd13bee574d242b_n.jpg&h=a54f76b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"356f9be06b76bca3c60fcb5a2702b2874ab0feb6","tid":824323,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64af02d5b9b1e290307b6ebe911f414fe69335c2","tid":824323,"uid":81037,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:10:58.000Z","msg":"王騎會唔會反埋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:21:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/029/52a/02952a89e5f90d6342dd1f3bb930857dda714701_n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2F029%2F52a%2F02952a89e5f90d6342dd1f3bb930857dda714701_n.png&h=80e18220&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb62b593513b04d3441b2e3d3ea832b4c32adad8","tid":824323,"uid":209138,"like":0